Forgive them even if they're not sorry.
Mediocrity will always try to drag excellence down to its level. Don't trade your superiority for their inferiority.
Decide that you want it more than you are afraid of it.
Sometimes it takes sadness to know happiness, noise to appreciate silence and absence to value presence.
I began learning long ago that those who are happiest are those who do the most for others. - Booker T. Washington
Tell someone they matter.

God only gives three answers to prayer:
1. Yes!
2. Not yet.
3. I have something better in mind.
Be positive, patient and persistent.
When love is real, it finds a way.
Good things come to those who believe, better things come to those who are patient, and the best things come to those who don't give up.
Faith consists in believing when it is beyond the power of reason to believe.
Don't let a bad day make you feel like you have a bad life.
Live in the moment. Forget the past and don't concern yourself with the future.
The greatest mistake we make is living in constant fear that we will make one.

✔ Alive
✔ Blessed
✔ Grateful
Beautiful things happen when you distance yourself from negativity.
Thank your past for all the lessons, and move on.
If you're brave enough to say goodbye, life will reward you with a new hello.
Why try and be fake when being real takes less effort?
Good times become good memories and bad times become good lessons.
No one has ever become poor by giving.
Don't say "I can't because I'm weak". Say "I may be weak, but I'm strong with God."
Do the best you can until you know better. Then when you know better, do better.
You know all those things you've always wanted to do? You should go do them.
It's better to be slapped by the truth than kissed with a lie.
Don't hate what you don't understand.
For attractive lips, speak words of kindness. For lovely eyes, seek out the good in people. -Audrey Hepburn
Be the best you can be.
Be sure to taste your words before you spit them out.
Never be afraid to try something new. Remember, amateurs built the ark. Professionals built the Titanic.
Sometimes you gotta fall before you fly.
